verbose_text: On the other hand, high IgG titers induced by two shots of rSAG1/2 (Vet L-10) during the first four weeks (P < 0.05, LDS multiple comparison) then gradually decreased to the levels before immunization from week 4 to week 12 (P < 0.05, LDS multiple comparison).
evidence: IgG titers induced by two shots of rSAG1/2
